{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act31side", "eventName": "懷黍離", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HS-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "織錦緞", "storyInfo": "黍犧牲了自己的生命來清除大荒城地底的邪魔污染。就當人們以為威脅散去的時候，績將一株被邪魔污染的水稻投入了大荒城的核心能源。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經丑時了……這局是誰贏了？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己數數。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都說過，我不擅長這事。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你應該學學。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要見你一面可不容易。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這古寺深寒，二哥倒是不改其道……你天天把自己關在這屋子裡對著這副棋盤，到底在上面看出什麼來了？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和你在那帳本上看到的，差不多。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "棋盤上有同一種規則，棋盤外，也是一樣。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天下熙熙，皆為利來；天下攘攘，皆為利往……二哥琢磨得通透。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些年來，兄弟姐妹幾個，自從找到各自感興趣的事後，好像都活得越來越愜意了。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老頭子好像終於參透了“武道”，轉身去北疆守城，大姐一夢千年四處神遊，好不自在。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是……除了那個姐姐。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多少年來……我還是為她不值。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#2$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來是你最近的生意做得太順，才有功夫操心這麼多事。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是最近才想明白一個道理，學會了一種活法。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天地者，萬物之逆旅也，光陰者，百代之過客也……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人活一世，無非是找到一處寄託，名心不化，這一生也就過去了。壽命長短，也無所謂什麼差別。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要是真的看透了，就不會坐在這。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你想說什麼。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想做的事，我能幫你。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我也要借你一樣東西。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二哥何必客氣，只要是我有的，需要什麼拿去就是。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把你的命給我。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g7_fieldhouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "聽說，我是從外面的村落來到大荒城的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那一年，有人在水田裡撿到了一個木盆，裡面裝著一個還不太會說話的孩子。大概是順著城外的大河漂到了水田裡。幸好被人撿到。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "想到之前傳來天災的消息，上游發生的事，似乎也不難猜。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你運氣真好。花下一禾生……就叫你“禾生”吧。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以後你就留在這吧。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_mini01_villagevacancy", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "後來，我四處打聽，想要找到我出生的村子。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我見到了一片空無一人的“村落”，眼前盡是破敗的房屋，源石晶簇遍佈的土地。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這裡的人，都去哪了？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的土地，種不出莊稼了。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為什麼……？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到那些黑色的石頭了嗎，有這些東西在的地方，糧食長不出來。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "種不出糧食，就有人要餓肚子。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "像這樣的土地……還有很多？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "有沒有辦法，讓這些壞石頭都消失，讓這片土地上長出作物？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有許多人，許多年來都在想辦法。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想要學習嗎？", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "嗯……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這可能會花很多時間，可能你付出了一生的努力，都不會看到結果。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便如此，你也不後悔嗎？", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "嗯。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g2_desertedcityfield_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_rain", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainlight_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近發生了許多事，原本熟悉的土地彷彿已經變成了人們不認識的樣子。古老的田地馬上就要完成翻新，又偏偏天意弄人，災異不斷。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "田邊頹坐的職農抬起頭，雨水落在他的臉上，清涼，溫和。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "田裡伏倒的莊稼也挺直了腰桿，枝葉變回了青翠的綠色。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1249_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是……", "name": "驚訝的職農"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1249_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神農，是神農……", "name": "驚訝的職農"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1249_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神農真的回來了……", "name": "驚訝的職農"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1249_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g4_factory_outside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你怎麼躺在這？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醒醒，喂，醒醒！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別跑！", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼又換上這身衣服了……？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……現在是什麼時候？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離我們上次碰面過去了半天，你讓我去查糧倉裡的莊稼，還說自己要去找把大荒城搞得滿城風雨的罪魁禍首——怎麼倒在這了？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那現在呢！", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糧倉裡的莊稼有沒有被污染，找到污染源在哪裡了嗎？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一點都沒看到……？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去到糧倉，發現之前夏收收上來的莊稼全都變成了詭異的紅黑色……不止這個，田裡的地都變成了板結的鹽鹼地。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可不知道怎麼回事，剛剛下了一場雨，土地全都恢復原狀，糧倉裡的糧食也變成了正常的樣子。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就好像，有誰用了誇張的源石技藝，把污染全都清除了。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地下的污染？誰能做到這種事……？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#3$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在，應該安全了？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#3$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場雨……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#3$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍在哪裡？！", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說……誰？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的老師呢？她在哪？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}},