rop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳咳……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小夕……你在畫裡待了那麼長時間，心氣還這麼浮躁，這可不是當世第一的畫家該有的心境吧。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有年，這麼長時間，我還從來沒見過你這麼認真的樣子，原來你還是很在乎自己的兄弟姐妹的。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會殺了你。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我說過，我是來幫你們的……咳咳……你們為什麼，就不相信呢？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們不是想要做成這個，能支持我們存在的能量的容器？“巨獸的心臟”？我來告訴你們它缺少什麼東西。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別過來。如果還想要命的話。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在實在不太有功夫來解開這個誤會……只能稍微委屈你們一下了。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hvygnthrtbt", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.7, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g5_factory_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g5_factory_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 5.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_nhvyprtn", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼能控制這個裝置？你是什麼時候——", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的能力本就是同源的，何況在怎麼對付自己的分身上，我專門學習了一些經驗。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$b_char_defboost", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1", "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.6, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#5$1", "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.6, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多少是有些冒險的辦法，會有些副作用，也是無可奈何。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也該大荒城有這麼一劫，總不能自己種下的惡因，最後全靠別人付出生命來收這個惡果……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哪有這樣便宜的好事。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#5$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人伸出手，一株漆黑的稻穗出現在掌中。"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“形”“意”“因果”，你們三人加起來，聽起來確實能做出一些逆天改命的事。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐她永遠是這樣，相信只要辛苦耕種灌溉，總能得出善果。相信這世上美多於醜，善多於惡。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可為什麼生命降生時，總是伴隨著啼哭？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人也好，獸也罷，羈弱的生命來到這蒼茫世上，感知到的第一種情緒，只能是恐懼。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該醒來了。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人將黑色的稻穗投入身前巨大的裝置。"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊接著，一顆心臟跳動起來。"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hvygnthrtbt", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}